today_comment: Locations closer to the reservoir will see MODERATE to USG conditions all day.

forecast_summary: Strong NE winds at terrain height expected to keep smoke aloft. Expect generally hazy conditions throughout the day.
today_comment: Primary smoke impacts expected to remain at terrain height with generally GOOD air quality at the surface.

extended_comment: Flow from the ocean towards the LA Basin expected to increase relative humidity values and suppress new fire activity and smoke production.
